---
title: Figure 3.8 — Diagramme de séquence — Caution, exécution et validation
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Prestataire
    actor Client
    participant FE as Angular
    participant API as Django REST
    participant ESC as EscrowService
    participant Chat as ChatService
    participant Track as TrackingService
    participant Proof as ProofService
    participant AI as AnalysisService
    participant WS as WebSocket<br/>Channels
    participant Notif as NotificationService
    participant MM as MetaMask
    participant SC as EscrowContract

    Note over Prestataire,SC: Étape 6: Exécution mission

    Prestataire->>FE: 6️⃣ Démarrer la mission
    FE->>API: POST /api/missions/{id}/start/
    API-->>FE: status=in_progress
    API->>Notif: send_notification(mission_started)
    
    Prestataire->>Chat: Envoyer message initial
    Chat->>WS: Broadcast message
    WS-->>Client: Message reçu en temps réel

    loop Suivi GPS continu
        Prestataire->>Track: Envoyer position GPS
        Track->>WS: gps_location_update
        WS-->>Client: Mise à jour carte temps réel
        Note right of Client: Suivi trajectoire<br/>Points de contrôle<br/>ETA estimé
    end

    Prestataire->>Chat: Communications ongoing
    Chat->>WS: message_exchange
    WS-->>Client: Notifications chat

    Note over Prestataire,SC: Étape 7: Soumission preuves

    Prestataire->>FE: 7️⃣ Capturer preuves
    FE->>Proof: upload_proof(photo_before)
    Proof->>AI: analyze_photo_quality()
    AI-->>Proof: blur_score, brightness, fraud_detection
    Proof-->>FE: proof_uploaded + analysis_results
    
    Prestataire->>FE: Capturer photo pendant
    FE->>Proof: upload_proof(photo_during)
    
    Prestataire->>FE: Capturer photo après
    FE->>Proof: upload_proof(photo_after)
    Proof->>AI: verify_mission_completion()
    
    Prestataire->>FE: Ajouter signature numérique
    FE->>Proof: upload_signature()
    
    Prestataire->>FE: Scanner QR code (si requis)
    FE->>Proof: validate_qr_code()
    
    Prestataire->>FE: 7️⃣ Finaliser soumission
    FE->>API: POST /api/missions/{id}/submit_proof/
    API->>Proof: validate_checklist_complete()
    API-->>FE: status=submitted
    API->>Notif: send_notification(proofs_submitted)

    opt Ancrage preuves on-chain
        FE->>MM: submitProof(missionId, proofHashes[])
        MM->>SC: batchTransaction(proofs)
        SC-->>MM: proofAnchored, txHash
        FE->>API: POST /api/escrow/blockchain/record-proofs/
        API-->>FE: blockchain_proofs=true
    end

    Note over Prestataire,SC: Étape 8: Validation client

    Client->>FE: 8️⃣ Vérifier preuves soumises
    FE->>API: GET /api/missions/{id}/proofs/
    API-->>FE: Liste preuves + analyses IA
    
    Client->>FE: Examiner photos et signatures
    FE->>Proof: display_proof_details()
    
    alt Validation manuelle
        Client->>FE: Approuver mission
        FE->>API: POST /api/missions/{id}/validate/
    else Auto-validation (24h)
        API->>API: schedule_auto_validation(24h)
        Note over API: Timer déclenché<br/>Validation automatique
    end

    Note over Prestataire,SC: Étape 9: Paiement final

    API->>ESC: release_payment_to_provider()
    ESC->>ESC: calculate_commission(5%)
    ESC->>ESC: transfer_95%_provider()
    ESC->>ESC: transfer_5%_platform()
    
    API->>API: update_reputation_scores()
    API->>Notif: send_notification(mission_completed)
    API-->>FE: status=completed ✅
    
    opt Ancrage final on-chain
        FE->>MM: completeMission(missionId, rating)
        MM->>SC: finalizeMission()
        FE->>API: POST /api/escrow/blockchain/record-completion/
    end

    FE-->>Client: Mission terminée<br/>Paiement effectué
    FE-->>Prestataire: Mission complétée<br/>Fonds reçus (95%)
    
    Note over Client,Notif: Cycle mission terminé ✅
